About this item

  • Materials and Design: The adapter is made with anti-interference zinc alloy metallic housing and minimalist design with anti-slippery embossments

  • Compatibility: This USB C to USB 3.0 adapter is compatible with iPhone 15/15 Plus/15 Pro/15 Pro Max and MacBook Pro after 2016 and MacBook Air after 2018 and most of the laptops, tablets and smartphones with a USB Type C port

Product Description

5Gbps Transmissions

  • The adapter can transfer data with speed up to USB 3.0 level from 480Mbps to 5Gbps.
  • The internal engineering design solves the problem of the interference between USB 3.0 and Wifi 2.4GHz signal. Some USB 3.0 devices stop working because of the interference, which won't happen on this adapter.

USB On The Go

  • Read information directly from a USB stick.
  • Plug and work, you can easily connect the phone to transfer data and charging.
  • The adapter connects USB cables, flash drives, mouse, keyboards, and other USB peripherals to your laptops and smartphones with USB-c ports.

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

      5.0 out of 5 stars Streamlined Connectivity: A Practical USB C to USB Adapter for Mac Users
      Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
      Color: Space GreyVerified Purchase
      After recently acquiring a larger USB C hub for my Mac, I found myself in need of a simpler solution for connecting individual accessories. The USB C to USB Adapter turned out to be the perfect complement, offering convenience and efficiency for straightforward connectivity needs.

      This adapter is a no-frills solution designed for simplicity, making it an excellent choice for users who only need to connect a single USB accessory to their Mac. It serves as a practical alternative to a larger hub when dealing with minimal peripheral devices.

      The setup is straightforward just plug the USB C end into your Mac, and you're ready to connect a standard USB accessory. I appreciate the adapter's plug-and-play functionality, eliminating the need for any complicated installation processes. It seamlessly integrates with my Mac, ensuring a hassle-free experience.

      One of the noteworthy aspects of this adapter is its compact design. It's incredibly portable and doesn't add any bulk to my setup. This makes it an ideal accessory for those on the go or for individuals who prefer a clean and minimalistic desk space.

      While it may not have the extensive port variety of a larger hub, this USB C to USB Adapter excels at what it's designed for providing a quick and efficient solution for connecting standard USB accessories. It's particularly handy for users who occasionally need to connect devices like USB drives, mice, or keyboards without the need for a full-fledged hub.
